  99:SynaptiX_FDK/board/sx_board.h ****      *       (e.g. overcurrent cutoff) until this is resolved.
 100:SynaptiX_FDK/board/sx_board.h ****      *
 101:SynaptiX_FDK/board/sx_board.h ****      * AIN2 = adc_vol (voltage-sense input, 12V rail through a resistor
 102:SynaptiX_FDK/board/sx_board.h ****      *   divider: R14=100K top / R15=20K bottom per schematic, confirmed
 103:SynaptiX_FDK/board/sx_board.h ****      *   with user — the divider node feeds AIN2 directly).
 104:SynaptiX_FDK/board/sx_board.h ****      *   Vout = Vin * 20k/(100k+20k) = Vin/6 -> 2.0V at 12V nominal,
 105:SynaptiX_FDK/board/sx_board.h ****      *   2.5V at a 15V worst-case rail — comfortably under both this
